snippet.title: Azu-Cola [あずこら] Game Sample - PC/Doujin
snippet.description:
Original Air Date: January 31, 2010

It's basically Azumanga characters in a Columns-style game. Not entirely sure why the game is called "Azu-Cola" though (Azumanga + Columns = Azu-Columns). Enjoy.
